      <title>伊姆兰·汗的政党敦促国际货币基金组织在谈判中考虑巴基斯坦的不稳定局势——消息人士</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/imran-khans-party-urges-imf-consider-pakistans-instability-talks-sources-2024-02-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两名知情人士周三表示，巴基斯坦被监禁的前总理伊姆兰·汗所在的政党已要求国际货币基金组织在任何进一步的救助谈判中考虑该国的政治稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/imran-khans-party-urges-imf-consider-pakistans-instability-talks-sources-2024-02-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 12:00:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿布扎比主权基金今年将投资太空技术和人工智能</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/abu-dhabi-sovereign-fund-invest-space-tech-ai-this-year-2024-02-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿布扎比穆巴达拉投资公司董事总经理周三表示，今年将向人工智能和太空技术投入大量资金，并承诺该主权财富基金将在美国进行更多投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/abu-dhabi-sovereign-fund-invest-space-tech-ai-this-year-2024-02-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 11:10:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马来西亚法院恢复对前总理穆希丁滥用职权的指控</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/malaysia-court-reinstates-abuse-power-charges-against-ex-pm-muhyiddin-2024-02-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据国家通讯社马新社报道，马来西亚上诉法院周三恢复了对反对党领袖和前总理穆希丁·亚辛滥用权力的指控。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/malaysia-court-reinstates-abuse-power-charges-against-ex-pm-muhyiddin-2024-02-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 10:59:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登将打击美国数据流向中国和俄罗斯</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/biden-crack-down-us-data-flows-china-russia-2024-02-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国高级官员表示，出于国家安全考虑，总统乔·拜登政府周三公布了一项行政命令，旨在通过限制向中国、俄罗斯和其他国家传输美国个人数据来保护美国个人数据。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/biden-crack-down-us-data-flows-china-russia-2024-02-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 10:02:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国在医生抗议下将派遣军医前往医院</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-send-military-doctors-hospitals-amid-doctors-protest-2024-02-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总理韩德洙周三表示，在实习医生大规模罢工后，韩国将在未来几天内派遣军队和社区医生前往医院，作为支持医疗保健系统的紧急措施的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-send-military-doctors-hospitals-amid-doctors-protest-2024-02-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 09:24:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>情报局长表示，澳大利亚政客向外国间谍团伙“出卖”了国家</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-intelligence-chief-reveals-details-foreign-spy-operation-2024-02-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[该国间谍负责人周三表示，一名前政客将澳大利亚“出卖”给了外国情报机构，并补充说，他的机构已与间谍团伙对峙，让他们知道他们的身份已被揭穿。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-intelligence-chief-reveals-details-foreign-spy-operation-2024-02-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 09:13:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>导演称奥斯卡提名的《前世》的灵感来自于移民经历</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/lifestyle/oscar-nominated-past-lives-was-inspired-by-immigrant-experience-director-says-2024-02-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩裔加拿大导演席琳·宋 (Celine Song) 在周三在韩国电影院上映前表示，奥斯卡提名电影《前世》的灵感源自她的移民生活。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/lifestyle/oscar-nominated-past-lives-was-inspired-by-immigrant-experience-director-says-2024-02-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 08:38:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲国家考虑在大流行关闭后重新开放驻朝鲜大使馆</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/european-countries-eye-reopening-embassies-north-korea-after-pandemic-closures-2024-02-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国代表团自朝鲜大使馆在疫情期间关闭以来首次访问朝鲜首都平壤，而其他欧洲国家则在为预期的回归做准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/european-countries-eye-reopening-embassies-north-korea-after-pandemic-closures-2024-02-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 08:38:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>专家称朝鲜第一颗间谍卫星“活着”，可以机动</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/north-koreas-first-spy-satellite-is-alive-can-manoeuvre-expert-says-2024-02-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位荷兰太空专家周二表示，朝鲜的第一颗间谍卫星“还活着”，此前检测到其轨道变化表明平壤成功控制了这颗航天器，但其能力仍不得而知。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/north-koreas-first-spy-satellite-is-alive-can-manoeuvre-expert-says-2024-02-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 07:09:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾特使表示，特朗普担任总统期间印太立场没有变化</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/no-change-indo-pacific-stance-under-trump-presidency-says-philippine-envoy-2024-02-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾长期驻华盛顿大使周三表示，如果唐纳德·特朗普赢得 11 月份的总统竞选，美国的印太战略不太可能改变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/no-change-indo-pacific-stance-under-trump-presidency-says-philippine-envoy-2024-02-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 06:10:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
